dev.jeka.core.api.depmanagement

Class JkMavenMetadata

  • java.lang.Object
    • dev.jeka.core.api.depmanagement.JkMavenMetadata

  • public final class JkMavenMetadata
extends java.lang.Object
    Object representation of the maven-metadata.xml file found in Maven repositories for describing available timestamped snapshot available for a given version. This is a not used for Maven2 repositories.
